Comments: 45 pages, extended version. to appear in Commun. Math. Phys.,

communicated with A. ConnesJournal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 209 (2000) 757-783

We introduce a new invariant for foliations using the even pairing betweenK-homology and cyclic homology and discuss some possible applications inphysics.